profile_summary: I'm Rossana Suarez, a seasoned Tech Lead DevOps with extensive expertise in scalable systems, cloud computing, and cutting-edge technologies. As a Docker Captain, GitLab Hero, and AWS Hero, I've developed a unique blend of technical skills, including proficiency in TypeScript, Go, and JavaScript. With over 226 public repositories and 599 followers, I've built a professional network and influence in the tech community. My work revolves around designing and implementing highly efficient and reliable systems, leveraging tools like Kubernetes, Terraform, and GitHub Actions. I'm passionate about innovation, and my mantra "No se puede crecer si no estas dispuesto a saltar a la zona de peligro" encapsulates my approach to embracing challenges and driving growth. When not coding, you can find me exploring the outdoors, traveling, or catching up on the latest series – always looking for inspiration and opportunities to grow.
